    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ピーピーピピッピー！　ピッピッピピッピー！　イェイ\nピーピーピピッピー！　ピッピッピピッピー！　イェイ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9666668098,
      "endTime": 8.8287531059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.1165918335
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9666666826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、大丈夫ですか？　昨日から取り憑かれたように\nホイッスルを吹き続けていて、ほとんど寝てませんよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9666666826,
      "endTime": 17.0432408175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.2333315691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "サンバというアイデアは面白いけど、それを活かした\n振り付けを考えるのが難しくて悩んでいるみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2333315691,
      "endTime": 24.761562999099997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.9516537508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "レコーディングの日も近いですから、振り付けは一旦\n後回しにして、曲だけ先に作ったらどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9516537508,
      "endTime": 31.9391594728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1516537508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "この曲はダンスが重要になるんだ。どうサンバを踊るか\nイメージすら定まらないのに曲を作る訳には……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1516537508,
      "endTime": 40.381267818,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14443.169053200001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5849863213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……ダメだ、頭が回らない\nちょっと温泉に入って頭を冷やして来るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5849863213,
      "endTime": 47.7249864739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9183196546
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "温泉に入ってものぼせるだけで頭は冷えませんよ！？\n……って、行っちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9183196546,
      "endTime": 55.2469818593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3183196386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "最近の葵さん、なんだからしくないですよね\n余裕がない感じで……一体どうしたんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4516529879,
      "endTime": 64.5016529879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.8433551565
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.7349863213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "まいったな。僕から曲作りをしたいと言い出したのに\n全然うまくいかないや……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7849863213,
      "endTime": 74.7349864167,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8266.653704299997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9516529879
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいたのね\n温泉に行ってもいなかったから、探したわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9516529879,
      "endTime": 80.11165312130001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.301743873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "莉央……\nよく僕がここにいるって分かったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.301743873,
      "endTime": 85.4217440446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.6350772064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "何年の付き合いだと思ってるの？\n相棒の行きそうな場所くらい察しが付くわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6350772064,
      "endTime": 91.4424014251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.6324921768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "この場所、懐かしいわ\nこの広場で四人でダンスの練習をしたこと、覚えてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6324921768,
      "endTime": 99.18682328870001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.3769140403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。リズノワを知らない通りすがりの人達が\n僕達のダンスを見て拍手をしてくれたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3769140403,
      "endTime": 107.6369140784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.8435807069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、愛とこころのおかげで\n私と葵は忘れかけていた情熱を取り戻した……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8435807069,
      "endTime": 114.6463244278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.8364151795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "本当の意味で四人体制のリズノワが始まったのは\nこの場所からかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8364151795,
      "endTime": 121.3941022712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.5841930229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "……あの時感じたような情熱を\nダンスで表現するには、どうしたらいいのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5841930229,
      "endTime": 128.6101566154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.8175263563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けで悩む葵を見ていて思ったけど\n私から言わせてもらえば……最近の葵は考え過ぎなのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8175263563,
      "endTime": 137.0005424657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.1906332174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "あれこれ悩んでないで、もっと自由に踊りなさい\nその方が葵らしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1906332174,
      "endTime": 143.2238080183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.4138987699
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "その言い方だとまるで\n僕がいつも何も考えていないみたいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4138987699,
      "endTime": 148.4898625532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.6805654365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_04-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "いいから。ほら、向こうに踊ってる子供達がいるわよ\nあそこに飛び込んで、一緒に踊ってきなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
